patthana8.65:1.1: Nasukhasahagataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nasukhasahagato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana8.65:2.1: Nanasukhasahagataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nanasukhasahagato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana8.65:3.1: Nasukhasahagatañca nanasukhasahagatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca nasukhasahagato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
patthana8.65:4.1: Hetuyā nava …pe… purejāte āsevane cha …pe… avigate nava.
